##### Header for General commands #####
atom_style granular
boundary f f p 
units si
communicate single vel yes
newton off 

##### Definition of simulationbox #####
region simulationdomain block ${xmin} ${xmax} ${ymin} ${ymax} ${zmin} ${zmax} units box
create_box ${nparticletype} simulationdomain
neighbor	0.00024 bin
neigh_modify	delay 0

##### write restart #####
shell mkdir restart
write_restart   ./restart/restart.bk1

